title: JAN 07 2022 - PRESIDENT BIDEN’S MOST HOLLOW PROMISE
description:
On today’s episode of Human Events Daily, Jack Posobiec asks, what happened to President Biden’s ‘Winter of Death for the Unvaccinated’. The Seattle police department faked a report of a right wing attack during CHAZ. The Police storm Tim Pool show live on air, and homeownership dreams of zoomers and millennials shattered by prices.

Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
